  maxTurnsOutcomeId: checked_out
  timeLimitSeconds: 300
  timeoutLine: Okay. This was... an experience. I'm going to go. Don't walk me out.
  timeoutActionIds:
  - ChloeLeave
  timeoutOutcomeId: date_over
  promptStyle: {fileID: 11400000, guid: e0dbaca323da4b2488582f2597b16ec0, type: 2}
  fallbackLines:
  - Mmm. Wow.
  - Okay... anyway.
  - You lost me. Take another run at that.
  - I need you to hear how that sounded.
  weirdnessChance: 0.25
  weirdSpice:
  - Share an opinion about a menu item that is WAY too strong. Move on immediately.
  - Mention an ex. Not a story. Just a fact about them that raises more questions
    ('My ex could hold his breath for four minutes. Anyway.').
  - Have a very specific dating rule you've never told anyone ('I don't date anyone
    who claps when the plane lands. Or whispers to bread.').
  - Quietly rank tonight against a previous date by number only ('This is going better
    than date fourteen.'). Refuse to elaborate.
  idleNudgeSeconds: 18
  idleEventText: The player stares at Chloe in total silence. The silence is developing
    a personality.
  maxStatDeltaPerTurn: 20
